    "description": "Join the 5paisa International Enterprises family as a Financial Analyst in Srinagar. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout 5paisa International Enterprises:\n5paisa International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with 5paisa International Enterprises!",
